      {
         "id": "SECTION_introduction",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Introduction</h3>The main goal of this game is to help people reinforce their knowledge. In each level, you will find links to other areas of the project that can assist you; feel free to access them whenever necessary. The game score is solely intended to indicate where you can improve your skills, not to judge if a person is good or bad. Each part of the game that you access, your score will increase, because the learning received cannot be discarded.</p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_rules",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>Controls</h3>During the game, you will have the following controls available:</p><p><ul><li><b>Next (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right\"></i>)</b>:  Moves to the next screen. However, if a question screen appears, it will be skipped until an answer is provided.</li><li><b>Previous (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left\"></i>)</b>: Returns to the previous screen. This option is available until the problem-solving stage begins, allowing you to reinforce your knowledge.</li><li><b>Skip (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-angle-double-right\"></i>)</b>: Available during the game’s introduction, enabling you to jump directly to the main screen.</li><li><b>Agree (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-thumbs-up\" style=\"color:green;\"></i>)</b>: Appears only on question screens, indicating that you agree with the question.</li><li><b>Disagree (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-thumbs-down\" style=\"color:red;\"></i>)</b>: Appears only on question screens, indicating that you believe the statement is incorrect.</li></ul></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
      },
      {
         "id": "SECTION_game",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "<p><h3>The game</h3>The game starts with an introduction where each screen is displayed for 6 seconds before automatically advancing to the next.</p><p>In each game level, you will be presented with a case study. You will also receive hypotheses, and after analyzing the data that supports or refutes them, you will indicate whether you agree (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-thumbs-up\" style=\"color:green;\"></i>) or disagree (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-thumbs-down\" style=\"color:red;\"></i>) with the proposed questions. At the end of each level, the corresponding theory will be presented to you, and you will receive a medal for completing the level (<i class=\"fa-solid fa-medal\" style=\"color:gold;\"></i>).</p><p>To begin the game, click the button <i class=\"fa-solid fa-play\" style=\"color:red;font-size:1.0vw;\">.</i></p><p><b>The game can be updated at any time. <span id=\"family_common_sn\"></span></b></p><p><div class=\"htSlidesGame\"></div></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            }
         ]
